  "prompt": "What are good watches for men under $200?",
  "response": "There are several excellent watches for men under $200 that offer great style, durability, and functionality. Here are some popular options across different categories:\n\n### **Casual/Everyday Watches**\n1. **Timex Weekender** - Known for its minimalist design and interchangeable straps, it\u2019s versatile and affordable.\n2. **Casio MDV106 \"Duro\"** - A rugged dive-style watch with a classic look and water resistance up to 200m.\n3. **Seiko 5 SNK809** - A reliable automatic watch with a timeless design and a durable movement.\n4. **Swatch Originals** - Fun, lightweight, and colorful designs that are perfect for casual wear.\n\n### **Sport Watches**\n1. **Casio G-Shock DW5600** - A durable and iconic shock-resistant watch with a retro digital design.\n2. **Timex Ironman Classic 30** - A robust digital watch with a stopwatch, countdown timer, and water resistance.\n3. **Casio AE1200WH \"World Time\"** - A digital watch with a retro look and multiple time zone functionality.\n\n### **Minimalist/Style Watches**\n1. **Braun BN0032** - A sleek, Bauhaus-inspired design with a clean and modern aesthetic.\n2. **Skagen Aaren Kulor** - A Danish-designed watch with a minimalist dial and interchangeable straps.\n3. **MVMT Classic Minimalist** - Simple, yet stylish, with a focus on clean lines and subtle branding.\n\n### **Automatic Watches**\n1. **Orient Bambino** - A classic dress watch with a mechanical movement and elegant design.\n2. **Vostok Amphibia** - A unique and rugged Russian-made dive watch with an automatic movement.\n3. **Invicta Pro Diver 8926OB** - A budget-friendly yet solid automatic dive watch inspired by Rolex Submariner designs.\n\n### **Smartwatches**\n1. **Amazfit Bip Series** - Affordable smartwatches with long battery life, fitness tracking, and notifications.\n2. **Fitbit Inspire Series** - Sleek fitness trackers with watch functionality for those focused on health tracking.\n\nThese watches offer a mix of style, durability, and functionality while staying under the $200 price point. Your choice will depend on your personal style, lifestyle, and preferences!",
